    "summary": "I'm a senior art director and designer with 12 years of experience at W+K Amsterdam, currently working as ACD. I have full independence and responsibility when it goes down to creative decisions and client management, within the limit of the project I am assigned to.\n\nI believe in the importance of the craft at every stage of the creative process. \nI strive to make work that is insightful, that resonates with culture, that shows up in a innovative way, and hopefully that has a positive impact in the world. \nMy background in digital design and technology enables me to comfortably engage in creative tech discussions.\n\nEmpathy is crucial to my leadership style, as I support, protect, and challenge my teams while being receptive to personal needs and ambitions. \n\nOutside of work, I enjoy sports, science and tech, and soaking up the sun.",
