            "description": "Inspired by the brave and daring attitude of the Carrera Panamericana, Carrera has Racing written in its DNA. Under the new payoff \"Racing since 1956\", Carrera merges the fashion and the racing world, rediscovering its heritage and talking directly to those who choose to live in the fast lane of life.  This campaign will lay the foundations for Carrera's long-term global brand platform. Launching in key markets with OOH, global events, point of sale activations and online with banners, films, social media and a brand new website. \n\nIn line with the ATL campaign the new Carrera website embraces the brands DNA, bringing to life the racing attitude with big determined visuals and bold graphic elements. Product is at the forefront and the full product catalogue is bought to life with large images and intuitive interactions, ensuring a fast and clear navigation. A fashion editorial approach provides background to the brand and collections creating inspiring shareable content that ladders up to the racing attitude. Carrera - you  race or you don't. \n\n\nAWARDS\n===============\nCommunication Arts: Webpick of the day 16th July 2013:\nhttp://www.commarts.com/web-sites/carrera.html\n\nFWA Mobile: Mobile of the day 18th June 2013:\nhttp://www.thefwa.com/mobile/carrera\n\nSite Inspire: Selected site 10th May 2013\nhttp://www.siteinspire.com/websites/3622-carrera\n\nAwwwards: Site of the day 8th May 2013\nhttp://www.awwwards.com/web-design-awards/carrera-world-1\n\nARTICLES\n===============\nSmashing Magazine: Beautiful Typography Web Design 6th August 2013\nhttp://www.smashingmagazine.com/2013/08/06/beautiful-typography-web-design/\n",
